Pre-Game Insights: Pakistan are touring England for a four-match T20I series to prepare for the ICC Men’s T20 World Cup 2024.
England’s last assignment in T20 format was in December 2023, where they lost a series to the West Indies.
Jos Buttler will lead England, and Babar Azam will lead Pakistan.
Jofra Archer’s return from injury is a key point for England.
Both teams are experimenting with combinations ahead of the T20 World Cup.
Miscellaneous Highlights: The pitch at Headingley offers assistance to pacers with lateral movement.
Weather forecast predicts high chance of rain and cold temperature.
